quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  6,138,"Nabo baboolanga mbu; “Tsisolo tsino nende emimela chino ni omusilo. Shibanyala okhubilia tawe halali balia aba efwe khubachamiile”- khukhuboola khwabu butswa. Nende tsisolo tsiakanibwa okhuninwa khumikongo chiatsio. Nende tsisolo tsindi etsilarumbulilungwakho elira lia Nyasaye tawe. Bachishilanga Nyasaye obubeyi. Alibarunga akabakholanga ako."
  6,139,"Ne baboolanga mbu; “Ebia munda mwetsisolo tsino nibia abasatsa befu bonyene, ne abakhasi befu bakaanibwa.” Ne ni ili ifwile, babilia boosi halala. Nyasaye alibarunga khukababoolanga ako. Toto Ye ni Owamachesi po, Omumanyi muno."
  6,140,"Toto bamala okhusikha balia abera abana babu mubusilu nibabula obumanyi, mana nibakania bilia ebia Nyasaye wabu abakabile, khukhuchishilasa Nyasaye. Toto bo bakora, ne shibali abalunjifu tawe."
  6,141,"Naye niye waloonga emikunda chili nende emisala chilandanga – emilandula nende echilalandanga, nende mitende nende emimela chiebiamo bikabukhane, nende emizaituni, nende emikoma chifwanana nende chilafwanana. Lie ebiamo babio olwa bibulananga, ne inyanga yokhuchesa murusie eshihanwa shiabio. Ne mulekhonyela khukhusasia tawe. Toto Ye shiyachama abandu ba isasia tawe."
  6,142,"Ne mutsisolo yabakholela tsilia tsiokhuchinga emisiko, nende obulili. Lie khubilia bia Nyasaye abakabile, ne mulaloonda amaseenelo ka Shetani tawe. Toto ye ni omusuku wenyu owa habulafu."